---
title: Chopped Greek Salad with Cannellini Beans, Olives, and Toasted Pita
description: Take a trip to Greece with this traditional Greek Salad! Creamy cannellini beans are simmered in a Mediterranean-inspired garlic marinade, then served with tomato, feta, cucumber, olives, and warm pita strips.
